    <h1>Eyecare - Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 12, 2026</p>
    <p>Eyecare ("we", "our", or "us") is developed by Firhan Studio. This Privacy Policy explains how our app handles your information.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Eyecare does <strong>not</strong> collect, store, or share any personal information. All settings (filter intensity, color tone, notification preferences) are stored locally on your device only.</p>

    <h2>Permissions Used</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW</strong> — Required to display the blue light filter overlay on your screen.</li>
        <li><strong>FOREGROUND_SERVICE</strong> — Required to keep the filter running when the app is in the background.</li>
        <li><strong>POST_NOTIFICATIONS</strong> — Required to send 20-20-20 eye rest reminders.</li>
        <li><strong>VIBRATE</strong> — Required for vibration alerts during eye rest reminders.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All data is stored locally on your device using Android SharedPreferences. We do not have access to your data and it is never transmitted to any server.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Eyecare does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our app does not collect any information from anyone, including children under 13.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:tohsufirhan@gmail.com">tohsufirhan@gmail.com</a></p>
